  <bns:description>JDBC connection to the NYU Langone Oracle audit and compliance database. Every integration event is written here for HIPAA audit trail requirements, compliance reporting, and operational monitoring. Demo talking point: "Notice that this is a second database connector in the same process - this time Oracle instead of SQL Server. Boomi treats both identically. You swap the JDBC driver, point to a different host, and the rest is the same design pattern. Two databases, one process, zero custom code."</bns:description>
